        "ScenePath": "assembly:/_pro/scenes/missions/elegant/scene_llama.entity",
        "TileImage": "$($repository 0f4829d8-35f2-4dc5-b7e9-85009cc90c67).Image",
        "Description": "Good Morning, 47. Our client, a retired singer, has been invited over to Vinedo Yates for the performance of a lifetime. Cristina Dionisi, on the other hand, is trying to get rid of her purely out of fun. She has sent 3 ex-sleeper agents there beforehand to keep a lookout and eliminate the target once in sight. Our client already knows about it and has hired you to take them down. We only have about 6 minutes before she gets here. We won&apos;t get another shot at this once she does. Good luck, 47.",
